<style>
:root{
  --bg0:#070b12;
  --bg1:#0b1324;
  --text:#e8edf6;
  --muted:#a9b3c7;
  --gold:#caa246;
  --line: rgba(202,162,70,.28);
  --stroke: rgba(255,255,255,.08);
  --stroke2: rgba(255,255,255,.12);
}

.ffm-wrap{
  min-height:100vh;
  background:
    radial-gradient(1000px 700px at 50% -10%, rgba(255,255,255,.10), transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(900px 700px at 50% 15%, rgba(202,162,70,.10), transparent 65%),
    linear-gradient(180deg, var(--bg0) 0%, var(--bg1) 55%, var(--bg0) 100%);
  color:var(--text);
  padding:clamp(24px,4vw,56px) 18px 80px;
}

.ffm-container{max-width:980px;margin:0 auto;}
.ffm-center{text-align:center;}
.ffm-gold{color:var(--gold);}

.ffm-divider{
  height:1px;
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--line),transparent);
  margin:40px auto;
  width:min(720px,92%);
}

/* Subtle fade-up animation */
@keyframes fadeUp {
  from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(18px); }
  to { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
}
.ffm-animate {
  opacity:0;
  animation: fadeUp .8s ease forwards;
}
.ffm-animate-delay { animation-delay:.2s; }
.ffm-animate-delay2 { animation-delay:.35s; }

/* GOLD ACCENT BULLET BLOCK */
.ffm-sandList{
  margin:22px auto 0;
  padding:22px 26px;
  list-style:none;
  display:grid;
  gap:12px;
  width:min(720px,100%);
  text-align:left;
  border-left:4px solid var(--gold);
  background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(202,162,70,.08),rgba(0,0,0,.15));
  border-radius:6px;
}

.ffm-sandList li{
  font-size:18px;
  line-height:1.7;
  color:rgba(232,237,246,.92);
  padding-left:6px;
}

.ffm-sandClose{
  margin-top:26px;
  font-size:21px;
  line-height:1.5;
}

.ffm-sandClose .awake{
  color:var(--gold);
  font-weight:900;
}

.ffm-decision{
  margin-top:18px;
  font-size:19px;
  line-height:1.6;
  color:rgba(232,237,246,.85);
}

.ffm-btnRow{
  display:flex;
  justify-content:center;
  gap:12px;
  flex-wrap:wrap;
  margin-top:22px;
}

.ffm-btn{
  display:inline-flex;
  align-items:center;
  justify-content:center;
  padding:15px 24px;
  border-radius:12px;
  font-weight:900;
  text-transform:uppercase;
  font-size:13px;
  text-decoration:none;
  min-width:220px;
  border:1px solid var(--stroke2);
  color:var(--text);
  background:rgba(0,0,0,.18);
}

.ffm-btn.primary{
  background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(202,162,70,.95),rgba(202,162,70,.8));
  color:#0a0f18;
  border-color: rgba(202,162,70,.55);
}

.ffm-btn:hover{transform:translateY(-1px);}
</style>

<div class="ffm-wrap">
<div class="ffm-container">

<div class="ffm-divider"></div>

<section class="ffm-section ffm-center ffm-animate">
  <h2>THE LINE IN THE SAND</h2>

  <p style="max-width:820px;margin:0 auto 16px auto;">
    For over two decades, The Fight for Manhood has taken men on a journey.
  </p>

  <p style="max-width:820px;margin:0 auto 16px auto;">
    Not a retreat.<br>
    Not a pep talk.<br>
    <span class="ffm-gold">A line in the sand.</span>
  </p>

  <div class="ffm-animate ffm-animate-delay">
    <div style="font-size:18px;margin-bottom:6px;">Men come here to:</div>

    <ul class="ffm-sandList">
      <li>Break free from passivity</li>
      <li>Reclaim their authority</li>
      <li>Repair what’s been broken</li>
      <li>Engage their wives</li>
      <li>Connect with their children</li>
      <li>Stand for what they believe</li>
      <li>Walk with confidence under God</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="ffm-sandClose ffm-animate ffm-animate-delay2">
    They don’t leave the same.<br>
    <span class="awake">They leave awake.</span><br><br>

    They go home different.<br>
    They lead different.<br>
    Their families feel it.
  </div>

  <div class="ffm-decision">
    Will you stay divided — or step across the line?
  </div>

  <div class="ffm-btnRow">
    <a class="ffm-btn primary" href="/register/">Step Across the Line</a>
    <a class="ffm-btn" href="/program/">See the Battle Plan</a>
  </div>

</section>

</div>
